  <refnamediv>
    <refname>etl_scicos_realtime</refname>

    <refpurpose>etl_scicos_realtime</refpurpose>
  </refnamediv>

 <refsection>
    <title>Parameters</title>
    <variablelist>
      <varlistentry>
        <term>Do Realtime</term>
        <listitem>
          <para>
	  Enables Realtime behavior. The scicos solver realtime flag should be disabled. For higher process priority, scilab has to started as root.
         </para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
      <varlistentry>
        <term>Cycletime</term>
        <listitem>
          <para>
	  Cycletime in ms
         </para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
    </variablelist>
  </refsection>
  <refsection>
    <title>Description</title>

    <para> This Block changes the process priority of scilab/scicos to RT-priority. The realtime behavior is implemented by the function call clock nanosleep. </para>
  </refsection>


